		<hr size="1">The only thing I can suggest is to train in all the weapon skills available to you....i.e. piercing, 1hb, 1hs. But keep your slashing as your main weapon skill.</P><P>I was lucky to find a Centi SS for 5pp and I also use a Wakizishi of the Frozen skies fo slashing. I am now also using a Netherbian Unguis for piercing and some cheap hammer with stats, I forget which, for 1hb.</P><P>However, honestly, I only use my weapons when I don't feel like soloing these days. A bards power is in their songs. Granted, I would suck as a main tank in a group right now, but I wouldn't want to be one anyway.</P><P>This is my opinion. I am sure others will think otherwise. But hey, I am only level 36 atm.<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
