		<hr size="1">Battle Drummer's Main Gauche is a 1hp weapon, nice stats and 2.0 drum modifier, same as Combine Drums, the epic, Singing Short Sword is 1.8 modifier to all instruments so you can easily get equipment to duplicate or surpase the epic.</P><P>Battle Drummer's Main Gauche = Percussion 2.0<BR>Gem Inlaid Longsword = Percussion 1.4<BR>Troubadour's Mace = Brass 1.8<BR>Tear Shaped Ring = Stringed 1.8</P><P>There are a lot of items that double as instruments and a few that enhance singing as well, an Abalone Engraved War Mask, no drop of course, is a 1.8 mod to singing based tunes and a Shadowsong Cloak has a right click effect that's 1.9 mod to singing.  </P><P>The BDMG and GILS range from 8kpp to 14kpp depending on your server.  I've never seen the Tear Shaped Ring for sale but then I've only had my eye out for it for a few days now.<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
